      • getOverridingAnchorDateViews

        public java.util.List<AnchorDateView> getOverridingAnchorDateViews()
        Returns:
        the AnchorDateViews for the overriding anchor dates. Returns an AnchorDateView for each anchor date used for the stream's periodicity. For example, returns one AnchorDateView for monthly streams and two AnchorDateViews for twice-per-month streams.

      • getPayerDefaultAnchorDateViews

        public java.util.List<AnchorDateView> getPayerDefaultAnchorDateViews()
        Returns the AnchorDateViews for the payer's default anchor dates for the stream's periodicity. Returns an AnchorDateView for each anchor date used for the stream's periodicity. For example, returns one AnchorDateView for monthly streams and two AnchorDateViews for twice-per-month streams.
        Returns:
        an empty list if the payer has no default anchor dates for the stream's periodicity.

      • isOverrideAnchorDates

        public void setOverrideAnchorDates(boolean overrideAnchorDates)
        Sets whether the stream is overriding the anchor dates. If overrideAnchorDates is true, initializes the stream's overriding anchor dates to be the payer's default anchor dates.
        Parameters:
        overrideAnchorDates - Whether or not the stream has overriding anchor dates
